253
00:10:45,625 --> 00:10:46,875
A HUMMINGBIRD WITH A BELL?

254
00:10:46,958 --> 00:10:48,041
- A HUM-DINGER!

255
00:10:48,125 --> 00:10:49,250
- UH?

256
00:10:49,333 --> 00:10:50,541
- Both: AW, COME ON, GUYS.

257
00:10:50,625 --> 00:10:52,583
THAT JOKE WASN'T SO BAD,
NOW WAS IT?

258
00:10:52,666 --> 00:10:54,541
- ( men shouting )
- HEY, WATCH IT!

259
00:10:54,625 --> 00:10:55,541
- OW!
- HEY!

260
00:10:55,625 --> 00:10:57,041
- ( laughing )

261
00:10:57,125 --> 00:10:59,000
