HOW DO YOU LIKE THIS TRICK?

262
00:10:59,083 --> 00:11:00,458
- Mihoshi:
THAT'S NOT VERY NICE.

263
00:11:00,541 --> 00:11:01,458
- Kiyone:
YOU THINK THIS IS EASY?

264
00:11:01,541 --> 00:11:02,958
- ( laughs )

265
00:11:03,041 --> 00:11:04,958
- Both:
HOW ABOUT TIGHTROPE WALKING?

266
00:11:05,041 --> 00:11:06,416
- Mihoshi: HOW ABOUT
IF I JUMP THROUGH

267
00:11:06,500 --> 00:11:07,416
A CIRCLE OF FLAME?

268
00:11:07,500 --> 00:11:09,416
- TA-DA!
- ( screams )

269
00:11:09,500 --> 00:11:10,833
- ( men shout )

270
00:11:10,916 --> 00:11:11,833
- ( laughs )

271
00:11:11,916 --> 00:11:13,208
- YOU LEAVE ME NO CHOICE.

272
00:11:13,291 --> 00:11:15,250
I'LL HAVE TO DO
MY FIRE BREATHING ACT.

273
00:11:15,333 --> 00:11:16,541
- YOU CAN REALLY DO THAT?

274
00:11:16,625 --> 00:11:17,750
- YEAH, WITH ANY LUCK.

275
00:11:18,833 --> 00:11:20,583
- ( screams )
- ( men cheer )

276
00:11:20,666 --> 00:11:22,250
- HEY, THEY'RE NOT
THROWING STUFF.

277
00:11:22,333 --> 00:11:24,208
OOH-OOH-OOH, OOH-OOH-OOH.

278
00:11:24,291 --> 00:11:26,166
- I'M GONNA WET MY PANTS
FROM LAUGHING.

279
00:11:26,250 --> 00:11:28,250
- GUESS WHAT--
THEY LIKE THIS ONE, HUH?

280
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:29,625
( giggles )
- YEAH?

281
00:11:31,666 --> 00:11:32,916
- TERRIFIC.

282
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:35,083
THEY MAKE ME LAUGH
JUST AS MUCH NOW AS BEFORE.

283
00:11:35,166 --> 00:11:36,583
- ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
KIYONE?

284
00:11:36,666 --> 00:11:37,833
- I'LL SURVIVE.

285
00:11:37,916 --> 00:11:39,291
AND ANYWAY,
IT'S A SMALL PRICE TO PAY

286
00:11:39,375 --> 00:11:40,291
FOR MY PROMOTION.

287
00:11:40,375 --> 00:11:41,666
I GOTTA TELL YOU THOUGH,

288
00:11:41,750 --> 00:11:43,958
RYOKO SEEMS TO BE HAVING
WAY TOO MUCH FUN WITH THIS.

289
00:11:44,041 --> 00:11:45,708
HER SADISTIC SIDE
REALLY COMES OUT

290
00:11:45,791 --> 00:11:47,500
WHEN SHE HAS POWER
OVER SOMEBODY.

291
00:11:47,583 --> 00:11:48,916
- I'M NOT SO SURE
ABOUT THAT.

292
00:11:49,000 --> 00:11:50,708
SHE WAS TRULY
ENJOYING HERSELF.

293
00:11:50,791 --> 00:11:52,916
IT LOOKED LIKE SHE WAS LAUGHING
JUST THE WAY SHE USED TO

294
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,083
BACK ON EARTH.

295
00:11:54,166 --> 00:11:55,166
